<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">-&nbsp;<a style="line-height: 1.75;" href="https://docs.google.com/a/crossroads.net/document/d/14lOceKNlgONYB0RyKraUeklZI2JL-1_w-pgbHv7jt7E/edit">Chapel FAQ</a></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">-&nbsp;<a style="line-height: 1.75;" href="http://www.crossroads.net/my/care/weddings/weddingresources.htm">Resources for vows and sample ceremonies</a></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
